data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the serene town of Lakeview. This charming 2-story, 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom traditional house is a slice of paradise. One of the real gems of this property is the all-sports lake access. Imagine spending your days on the water, whether it's swimming, boating, or simply enjoying the beauty of the lake. The daytime dock use adds an extra layer of convenience to this fantastic feature. Outside, you'll find a deck at the back of the house, offering a wonderful space for outdoor dining, barbecues, or simply enjoying the peace and quiet of the wooded surroundings. The Lakeview community is known for its tranquil and friendly atmosphere, making it an ideal place to call home. You'll enjoy the company of kind neighbors and the tranquility of this beautiful area.
